{
  "texts": [
    "This study further opens several pathways for future research.",
    "One key area involves refining AI models, including ChatGPT, to better suit primary school contexts, ensuring they are tailored to the unique needs and learning styles of students across various age groups.",
    "Additionally, investigating the most effective methods for integrating AI technologies into teacher education programs presents a valuable direction.",
    "This includes exploring how educators can be trained to effectively use AI as a tool for enhancing teaching and learning experiences.",
    "Lastly, there is a significant opportunity to examine the impact of AI-based systems on student learning outcomes."
  ]
}